snippet.title: MORSE Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab the Demo Here: https://alexvscoding.itch.io/morse​

Break the bitter attrition of the Great War using timing, tactics and telecommunications in MORSE. Learn a lost language, wander the grounds between your shifts and get to know your colleagues. 

Dev Log: https://forums.tigsource.com/index.php?topic=48015.0
Follow the project: https://twitter.com/alexvscoding​
